Sentencas: Interconnects used in Solid Oxide Cells stacks require protective coatings to lower their parabolic rate constant and block chromium evaporation (on the air side).
Titulo: Evaluation of electrodeposited Mn-Co protective coatings on Crofer 22 APU steel

Sentencas: In this work four different protective coatings on steel are evaluated for their high temperature corrosion resistance and electrical conductivity.
Titulo: Evaluation of electrodeposited Mn-Co protective coatings on Crofer 22 APU steel

Sentencas: A commercial electroplating process was used for the preparation of coatings with different Mn/Co ratios on Crofer 22 APU steel.
Titulo: Evaluation of electrodeposited Mn-Co protective coatings on Crofer 22 APU steel

Sentencas: Oxidation of samples was performed in air at 800 degrees C for 1000 hours.
Titulo: Evaluation of electrodeposited Mn-Co protective coatings on Crofer 22 APU steel

Sentencas: Postmortem analysis of the coated samples was performed by scanning electron microscopy and x-ray diffractomettry.
Titulo: Evaluation of electrodeposited Mn-Co protective coatings on Crofer 22 APU steel

Sentencas: Based on the results, influence of the Co/Mn ratio on the resulting corrosion properties are discussed.
Titulo: Evaluation of electrodeposited Mn-Co protective coatings on Crofer 22 APU steel

Sentencas: Parabolic rate constant of the coated samples is the lowest for the MnCo sample, whereas electrical resistance is the lowest for the Co sample, which has a corrosion rate similar to the not-coated alloys.
Titulo: Evaluation of electrodeposited Mn-Co protective coatings on Crofer 22 APU steel
